    <div class="detail-tags"><span class="detail-tag">Python</span><span class="detail-tag">Raspberry Pi</span><span class="detail-tag">Computer Vision</span><span class="detail-tag">OpenCV</span><span class="detail-tag">PCB Inspection</span></div>
